## ğŸ§¯ Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| `No solution found` | Check linear independence of equations |
| Logic errors | Ensure Boolean expressions use correct digital syntax: `'` = NOT, `*` = AND, `+` = OR, `~` = XOR |
| PT100 out-of-range | Valid range: 0Â°C to 850Â°C |

